484
00:36:06,797 --> 00:36:08,286
You're English?

485
00:36:11,501 --> 00:36:12,992
And so are you.

486
00:36:13,538 --> 00:36:14,936
Indeed I am.

487
00:36:15,606 --> 00:36:18,403
- You here on a holiday?
